Note of BWA aligner

URL: http://bio-bwa.sourceforge.net/

Example: Illumina Sequencing Libray
Reference genome: Homo sapiens, UCSC hg19 (URL: http://hgdownload.cse.ucsc.edu/goldenPath/hg19/bigZips/chromFa.tar.gz)

1. Build index from reference genome
	bwa index ref.fa

2. Alignment with bwa-mem
	 bwa mem ref.fa read1.fq read2.fq | samtools view -bS -o peread.bam -
